      "span_text": "Thiols such as GSH interfere with the complex carcinogenic process by conjugating with electrophilic carcinogens (all carcinogens are highly electrophilic, and may attack electron rich sites on macromolecules, particularly DNA in target cells), thereby preventing tumor initiation and defending against oxidative stress"
